<section id="technology" class="content-section">
    <div class="section-header">
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Technology</span>
        <h2>Meet Our AI Agents</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">Unlike generic AI wrappers, our system utilizes specialized agents to ensure accuracy and eliminate hallucinations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="agents-grid">
        <div class="agent-card">
            <h4>Kevin (The Ingestor)</h4>
            <p>Handles the extraction of raw data from your documents, converting it into a standardized, normalized form without rephrasing or misinterpretation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card">
            <h4>Ingrid (The Analyst)</h4>
            <p>Maps your internal documents against complex regulations (like NIS2) to perform automatic gap analysis and draft compliance paperwork.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card">
            <h4>Philip (The Monitor)</h4>
            <p>Ensures quality control by evaluating results against strict thresholds. Philip provides confidence scores to ensure the system gets smarter over time and remains "bullet-proof" for auditors.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
.content-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
}
.section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
}
.eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.section-header h2 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}
.section-header .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 1rem auto 0;
}

.agents-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}
.agent-card {
    background: rgba(17, 17, 21, 0.4);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
}
.agent-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.agent-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
}
</style>